ltiple-level\nanalysis of jokes. Finally, a speculative theory about the adaptive value of\nhumor is presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2013 05:07:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2013 00:32:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2019 21:04:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-08"}
