 number of major merging events and is easily extended\nto large samples of clusters from future surveys which could potentially push\nstatistical errors to 0.1cm^2g^-1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2013 11:05:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2013 11:45:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
